## ğŸš¢ Container Recap
- Concept came from **shipping containers**:
  - Same size â†’ fits anywhere (trucks, ships, warehouses).
  - Easy & consistent transport worldwide.
- **IT containers**:
  - Package = Application code + Libraries + Configs (âš ï¸ no OS).
  - Portable across systems â†’ "runs on my computer" issue solved.
  - Multiple containers can run on one OS.

