## ğŸ—“ Docker History
- **2010** â†’ Started as internal project at dotCloud.
- **2013** â†’ Released as open-source.
- **2015** â†’ Introduced Docker Swarm (orchestration).
- **2020+** â†’ Focus on Docker Desktop, Hub, cloud-native workflows.

